Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:03.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nforourdreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aftertheirfight with Naraku\nwas over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}they had promised to marry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:17.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But because of Miroku, their\nrelationship totally deteriorates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you sure this is what\nyou want, Sango?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:22.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is still depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because a pickpocket stole\nhis wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could I have\nlet this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, don't take it\ntoo hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't be so kind\nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:27.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't forgive myself\nforbeing so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:29.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's being depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What he says and what he does\nare complete opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This charm was given to me\nby a man of high personage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please accept this and\nfind peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- An earthquake?\N- And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:03.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:04.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive us! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be troubled by\nsomething evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can be\nof some {\i1}help....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:24.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:30.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you come to fulfill\nyourpromise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to marry and become an\nadopted son-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adopted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk Miroku has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Begin the preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! He probably has\ntoo many things to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima!\NHow lovely you've become!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's something from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. And both my wife and I had\ngiven up hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,believing it was\na thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourdaughter, Shima, was always\nsickly and frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was never a day when
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she could lift her head\nfrom herpillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's when Monk Miroku\npassed through the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boil these herbs in\nclean water,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then drink the liquid\nevery day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And as one would expect from\nsuch a costly medicinal herb,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it worked so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was such an expensive medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a scam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two became fast friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He gave us the medicine,\nthen left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? I'm totally clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:06.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Except?\N- Except?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you are well,\nwill you bear my child?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:19.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The medicinal herb and the promise\NI made to Miroku sustained me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I recovered completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}were{\i0} trying to seduce her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, it's a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of all the stupid {\i1}things....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the big deal anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to the\nevil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The incidentearlier\nat the {\i1}shrine....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Anotherearthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so afraid, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared too...\NBut fora different reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:57.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk Miroku, please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If nothing is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ourdaughter will end up\nas the wife of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That shrine is dedicated\nto the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Masterhas demanded Shima\nto be his wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've told him that I am betrothed,\nbut he does not believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourbetrothed {\i1}is....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Miroku, you didn't forget\nourpromise and returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't know how I've\nwaited for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, we cannot hand over\NShima to the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let us prepare\nthe ceremony right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:52.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought he's gonna\ndestroy the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The other is that she intends\nto have Miroku's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:11.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima, this is our promised night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is Miroku the only one inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wonder....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said he was going\nto settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meaning he's going to turn\ndown the marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, Miroku promised\nto marry Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure you can trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is Miroku, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a foolish man who turns down\na woman who offers herself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the first place,\nwhen did you learn such vulgarities?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the second place, think about\nthe people around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm second place, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like you to marry my daughter\nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the Masterwho desires Shima\nis a demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whether she's married ornot,\nhe will come afterher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:22.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Master of the Lake wants\na virgin bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:26.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So if a marriage ceremony is held,\nwe think he will give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's noble of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before the demon comes,\nplease make me yourwife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shima....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a foolish man who turns down\na woman who offers herself to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monk....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A specter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was just trying to express\nhow you were feeling, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drop dead, you idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hereyes were shouting to me,\N"Drop dead, you idiot."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk {\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anotherearthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something smelly is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like the Master of the Lake\nis about to make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the Master of the Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have come for Shima\nas promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you interfere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The girl doesn't want you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:04.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, I'm frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She clearly promised to\nbe my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I neverpromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,P-Please forgive us, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To be {\i1}truthful....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:34.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in orderto boil\nthe expensive {\i1}herbs....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boil these herbs in\nclean water,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then drink the liquid\nevery day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I used the water from the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And at the same time, every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I prayed at the shrine\nby the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Masterof the Lake, please\nbring my daughterback to health.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will do anything in return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I neverimagined that the Master\nwas actually listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Master asked for\NShima in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel a bit sorry {\i1}forhim....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that my fathermade\nsuch a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:18.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:22.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did it all out of a desire\nto save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's nothing we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you didn't know the Master\nwas listening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a promise is still a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, so {\i1}you'll....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not {\i1}serious....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about becoming a demon's bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:37.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not fit to become yourwife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have heard that you desire\na virgin bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But two years ago, {\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,gave myself to Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Is that true, Shima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father.\NI couldn't bring myself to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But hearing it confirmed\nis still a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait {\i1}now....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's all in the past, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....{\i0} It's as you just heard, {\i1}so....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forget about this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You deceived {\i1}me....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Love spurned becomes\nintense hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agiant catfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will feel my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Our house will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, we'll tame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:58.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can take care of it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourpast indiscretion caused this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Is this lady going to transform\nfrom now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's not a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourhome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll swallow you whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me explain and you'll understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't {\i1}think....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,things are going to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not... Not going to work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going to happen\nto the two of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we be paying attention\nto Inuyasha and the catfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you make a fool out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:10.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you won'tgive up,\NI'm gonna get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shima....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has the Master of the {\i1}Lake....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,given up on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thatended quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't sleep well at night\nif I killed a demon like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But things have gotten very\nserious overthere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Are they still fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you even listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku's habit of flirting with women\ndidn't start yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the woman of his past appears\nbefore her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it's not a comfortable feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,E-Excuse {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't blame Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, aren't you going afterher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, she won't listen,\nno matter what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:43.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm very {\i1}saddened....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that she really didn't trust me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My heart is set on one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sound as though you've\nbeen falsely accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- S-Shima!\N- Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't forget you, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! We will live together\nat the bottom of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I should've delivered the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku... isn't coming afterme.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No!\N- You'll marry me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you that I gave myself\nto Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forget about your past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:58.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were with {\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not that he's coming afterme!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:33.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, take herto a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He deflected the Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman, I'll take you to the bottom\nof the lake too
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and make you my mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say that again!\NHow dare you take my woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're in the water!\NDo you think you can catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then get a taste of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Churn....churn....churn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wateris {\i1}disappearing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen up, catfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare mess with my girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Is she one of yours, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:48.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I guess there's nothing for\nme to do {\i1}here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it was a case of\nunrequited love forme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You lied aboutgiving yourself\nto Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't want to wed the catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the only thing\NShima could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:44.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Then why didn't you tell me the truth\nat least?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was too {\i1}naïve....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you'd understand\neven without my saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's because I'm always such a cad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I hurt you, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you saved {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was very {\i1}happy....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you forgive me, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That should be my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:22.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango has such a big heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In some ways, it's biggerthan\nyours, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You make a fine match, Miroku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he had told her the truth sooner,\nall this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or maybe, {\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it took you a long time\nto remember what was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:57.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bull's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true? Well, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it happened so long {\i1}ago....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin has been kidnapped by a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agroup of monks who specialize\nin slaying demons went to save her, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those monks don't like demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:57.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they come across Sesshomaru,\nthis could be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans can try their half-baked tricks,\nbut Sesshomaru will tear them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Foreverwith Lord Sesshomaru"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:12.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru, please don't forget me\neven if I die!
